A 8-bit CPU.

Can process 8 bits at a time, registers can hold value from 0-255.

Instructions

LOAD A  	0x01
MOVE A->B	0x02
ADD		0x03
HLT		0x04

Registers

A
B
PC (Program Count)

Memory

Memory contains instructions to add A,B in hex format. This memory is ready by the PC - taken each instruction and translated and does the working.

